1. *Skot* je često kasnio na sastanke. (Scott was often late for meetings.)
2. Kada je *scot* dobio posao, preselio se u drugi grad. (When Scott got a job, he moved to another city.)
3. Moj prijatelj se oženio sa *Scot*om iz SAD-a. (My friend married a Scott from the USA.)
4. *Skota* sam sreo u prodavnici juče. (I met Scott in the store yesterday.)
5. Kada sam išao u školu, *scotovi* su bili vrlo popularni. (When I was in school, Scotts were very popular.)
6. Danas ću posjetiti *skotovu* porodicu. (Today I will visit Scott's family.)
7. Čitam knjigu o *scotovima*. (I am reading a book about Scotts.)
8. *Skotu* se sviđa da putuje i istražuje nova mjesta. (Scott likes to travel and explore new places.)